學習規範 Course Policy
	    1.Mid-term
2.Final exam
3.Journal article reports:
(1). Two journal articles published by SCI journals (in 2008 and after), one in the industrial hygiene  (IH) field and the other in the environmental health (EH) field, must be selected for your reports.
(2). The article and your reports should be collected by TA on 11/15 (topic should be relevant to IH) and 1/10 (topic should be relevant to EH), respectively.      

