指導學生狀況（至少五年內）


指導學生-碩士論文名稱姓名船舶製造業焊接燻煙與反應性氧化物種逸散特徵及其應用(100年度)鄭曉蔓暴露芳香蠟燭燃燒產物對社會壓力誘導心肺傷害之影響（與 劉明毅 老師共同指導）(100年度)曾築涵重複油炸過程對食用油品品質及多環芳香烴化合物排放之影響（與 廖寶琦 老師共同指導）(100年度)林採蓁遊艇製造業作業勞工揮發性有機物長期暴露評估（與 廖寶琦 老師共同指導）(100年度)鄭姝涵芳香蠟燭燃燒時奈米微粒之逸散特徵(99年度)馮脩文食用油重覆油炸後之酸價與油品內含PAHs之變化情形及其對勞工呼吸道暴露之影響 (99年度)周晏如從肺部上皮細胞增生及免疫發炎反應之角度探討適用於不同粒徑石英粉塵之暴露評估指標（與 張志欽 老師共同指導）(98年度)許瑋婷噪音暴露勞工抗氧化能力與環境因子對噪音引起的聽覺影響（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(98年度)林政佑不同溼度情形下三氯矽甲烷逸散及燃燒時之鹽酸氣膠及酸性氣體逸散特徵(98年度)黎秀蓉我國事業單位局部排氣裝置設置現況、有效性與能耗情形之分析(97年度)賴彥宏螺絲製造業搓製程油霧滴多環芳香烴碳氫化合物、金屬與反應性含氧物種特徵之研究(97年度)林於娟燒結廠煙道戴奧辛氣固相分配特性之校正方法之研究(97年度)楊鎮壕芳香蠟燭使用時多環芳香烴化物與揮發性有機物之排放特徵評估(97年度)施巧玲螺絲製造業成型製程多環芳香烴化合物及金屬之逸散特徵(96年度)梁方熒台灣鹽工職業性負重與退化性膝關節炎 (95年度)蕭旭峰原料組成對鐵礦燒結製程重金屬排放特徵及其流佈之影響（與 牟金祿 老師共同指導）(95年度)謝艾芸鑽鑿作業產生之振動與粉塵之相關性探討(94年度)李世詮探討不同可呼吸性粉塵 採樣器所採集之粉塵在濾紙上分佈之均勻性及其對結晶型二氧化矽定量的影響(94年度)彭雅蓮石油焦作業勞工之多環 芳香烴化物暴露及健康危害風險評估(94年度)範燕婷電弧爐作業勞工之多環芳香烴碳氫化合物暴露危害評估(93年度)翁嘉成航空器引擎 PAHs 及 VOCs 排放特徵與維修及測試期間勞工暴露評估(92年度)陳裕政以異辛烷為汽油添加劑對機車引擎揮發性有機物及醛酮化合物 排放之影響(92年度)邱雅琪鑄造業勞工結晶型游離二氧化矽暴露特徵與健康危害風險評估(92年度)陳慶樺鋼鐵燒結工廠內空氣中戴奧辛之特徵及勞工暴露風險評估（與 李文智 老師共同指導）黃生龍都市垃圾焚化爐拆爐作業勞工結晶型二氧化矽暴露評估(91年度)盧保艮都市焚化爐拆爐作業員工之多環芳香烴碳氫化合物暴露危害評估(91年度)林昌億我國高科技與傳統工業職業災害率與災害原因之比較分析（與 蘇慧貞 老師共同指導）(91年度)洪綜禧精神醫療機構護理人員工作壓力之探討（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(90年度)沈秀娟台灣微電子工業從業人員工作壓力與肩、頸不適症狀之關係（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(90年度)張光喜靜止空氣環境中之人體吸入效率與採樣器效能探討(90年度)林少娟我國大專院校學生意外災害與安全衛生認知調查（與 蘇慧貞 老師共同指導）(90年度)杜婯嫥築爐員工游離二氧化矽暴露評估與健康效應評估（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(90年度)蘇雅鈞高速公路收費站人員及加油站作業員工揮發性有機物質之暴露危害評估（與 李俊璋 老師共同指導 ）(90年度)陳美如熱作業環境變項改善最佳化系統預估模式之研發(90年度)羅志綸瀝青拌合至鋪面過程各階段之PAHs逸散特徵與鋪面勞工之暴露評估（與 李文智 老師共同指導）(90年度)王櫻芳以最佳化分析技術選取高溫環境最佳控制策略（與 張乃斌 老師共同指導）(89年度)杜信弘高速公路收費站人員 PAHs 之暴露危害評估（與 李文智 老師共同指導）(89年度)陳小龍傢俱製造工廠勞工之呼吸道症狀、肺功能與木粉暴露之間的相關性（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(88年度)林炳賦耐火材料業勞工游離二氧化矽暴露危害與風險評估(88年度)蘇麗芳生理觀點之高溫作業熱危害評估模式之應用(88年度)吳豐任碳黑業勞工多環芳香烴碳氫化合物類 ( PAHs ) 之暴露調查及其健康危害風險評估（與 李文智 老師共同指導）(87年度)薛宏榮以採樣器及吸入效率之觀點探討環境風向對氣懸微粒採樣結果之影響(87年度)吳怡萱電池室酸性氣膠之特徵（與 李文智 老師共同指導）(86年度)郭益銘活性生物氣膠採樣器採樣特性評估（與 蘇慧貞 老師共同指導 ）(86年度)陳宇信ISO高溫作業熱危害評估模式對國內勞工適用性探討(86年度)謝榮裕二異氰酸甲苯與職業性氣喘發生關係性之評估（與 郭育良 老師共同指導）(86年度)高名人鉻電鍍工業勞工環境暴露與生物偵測結果之相關性探討(85年度)陳志郎顯示更多-博士論文名稱姓名應用貝氏決策分析技術建構整合式螺絲製造工廠油霧滴及多環芳香烴化合物暴露與健康風險評估(103年度)徐新益可呼吸性粉塵於濾紙之均勻性及石英粒徑對X光繞射儀直接分析方法之影響及新型握持器之開發研究(103年度)陳慶樺戴奧辛生成機制、廢氣氣固相分佈及多環境介質間流佈相關性研究（與 廖寶琦 老師共同指導）(100年度)郭昱傑應用Modified Electrical Aerosol Detector (MEAD)於現場奈米暴露評估之適用性探討及奈米發生源排放係數推估之研究（與 廖寶琦 老師共同指導）(100年度)王櫻芳以替代指標量測結果推估勞工暴露之研究(99年度)粟自強鐵礦燒結製程之PCDD/Fs及PAHs排放減量與勞工暴露源鑑定技術開發 (98年度)陳裕政螺絲製造業製程之油霧滴、及多環芳香烴化合物逸散特徵及其勞工之暴露危害評估(97年度)陳美如皮革製造業勞工二甲基甲醯胺皮膚暴露評估與二甲基甲醯胺經皮滲透與皮膚滯留之探討(97年度)王士旻焚化灰渣玻璃化之評估研究（與 李文智 老師共同指導）郭益銘顯示更多特殊榮譽1.      Best Research Paper Award for 2014 Taiwan Association for Aerosol Research (TAAR), " Young, L.-H., Lin, Y.-H., Lin, T.-H., Tsai, P.-J.* (Corresponding author), Wang, Y.-F., Hung, S.-M., Tsai, C.-J., Chen, C.-W., Field application of a newly developed personal nanoparticle sampler to selected metalworking operations. Aerosol and Air Quality Research, 2013, 13: 849–861." .2.      Best Paper Award in Industrial Safety and Health Techniques (First prize) for 2nd Workplace Safety and Health Forum, "Developing techniques for heath-risk assessment and alarm system for workers exposed to multiple chemical agents", Taichung, Taiwan, June 13rd, 2013. 3.      Best Paper Award in Industrial Safety and Health Technique Category in 2012 Industrial Safety and Health Technology Best Paper Competition, “Assessing Long-term Oil Mist Exposures to Workers in a Fastener Manufacturing Industry Using the Bayesian Decision Analysis Technique”, Council of Labor Affairs, Executive Yuan, July 4, 2012.- 4.      Best Paper Award in Industrial Safety and Health Techniques (First prize) for 1st Workplace Safety and Health Forum, "Developing Techniques for Control Banding and Health Risk Assessment for Workplace Chemical exposures", Taichung, Taiwan, May 31st, 2012.- 5.      Outstanding Research Award, "Correcting the Gas and Particle Partitioning of PCDD/F Congeners in the Flue Gas of an Iron Ore Sinter Plant", College of Medicine, National Cheng Kung University, May 31, 2012.- 6.      Outstanding Research Award, "Effects of Uniformities of Deposition of Respirable Particles on Filters on Determining Their Quartz Contents by Using the Direct on-Filter Z-ray Diffraction (DOF XRD) method", College of Medicine, National Cheng Kung University, May 31, 2012.- 7.      Best Paper Award in Industrial Hygiene (First prize) in 2012 International Occupational Hygiene Conference, “Effects of exposure to combustion products of scented candle on social stress-induced cardiopulmonary injury in mice”, Taiwan Occupational Hygiene Association. Apr. 27, 2012.- 8.      Best Paper Award, “Reducing PAH emissions from the iron ore sintering process by optimization its operation operators”. Cheng Hsing Medical Research and Teaching Foundation, July 25, 2011.- 9.      Best Paper Award in Industrial Safety Technique Category (Second prize) in 2011 Industrial Safety and Health Technology Best Paper Competition, “Acid Gas, Acid Aerosol and Chlorine Emissions from Trichlorosilane Burning Processes”, Council of Labor Affairs, Executive Yuan, July 5, 2011.- 10.  Best Paper Award in Industrial Safety and Health Management Technique Category (Second prize) in 2011 Industrial Safety and Health Technology Best Paper Competition, “Implementing a National Occupational Health Control Strategy by Combining a Semi-quantitative Risk Assessment Model and Bayesian Decision Analysis Technique”, Council of Labor Affairs, Executive Yuan, July 5, 2011.- 11.  Best Paper Award in Industrial Health Technique Category in 2011 Industrial Safety and Health Technology Best Paper Competition, “Developing a New Technique for Free Silica Exposure Assessment”, Council of Labor Affairs, Executive Yuan, July 5, 2011.- 12.  Best Reviewer Award (Vol.2, No. 1) of Safety and Health at Work (SH@W), Occupational Safety and Health Research Institute (OSHRI), Korea Occupational Safety and Health Agency (KOSHA), June 14, 2011.- 13.  Best Paper Award in Industrial Hygiene (First prize) in 2011 International Industrial Hygiene and Occupational Medicine Conference, “Can Acid Values of Cooking Oil be Used as an Index for Assessing Workers’ Exposures to PAHs emitted from Cooking Process”, Taichung, Taiwan, Apr., 2011.- 14.  Best Research Award in Health Science, “Reducing PAH emissions from the iron ore sintering process by optimization its operation operators”. National Cheng Kung University Medical College, Dec. 31, 2010.- 15.  Best Paper Award, “Determining Optimal Operation Parameters for Reducing PCDD/F emissions from the iron ore sintering process by Using the Taguchi Experimental Design”. Cheng Hsing Medical Research and Teaching Foundation, June 18, 2010.- 16.  Best Paper Award (First prize) in 2010 Industrial Hygiene and Occupational Medicine Conference, “Gene-Environmental Interaction in Noise–induced Permanent Threshold Shift”, Taipei, Taiwan, Mar., 2010.- 17.  Best Paper Award (Third prize) in 2009 Industrial Safety and Health Technology Best Paper Competition, “Analysis of Current Installation Condition, Energy Consumption and Effectiveness of Local Exhaust Ventilation System Used in Industries in Taiwan”, Council of Labor Affairs, Executive Yuan, July, 2009.- 18.  Best Paper Award (First prize) in 2008 Chinese Environmental Engineering Association Conference, “Determining Optimal Operation Parameters for Reducing PCDD/F Emissions (I-TEQ values) from the Iron Ore Sintering Process by Using the Taguchi Experimental Design”, Taipei, Taiwan, Nov., 2008.- 19.  Best Paper Award in International Occupational Hygiene Association (IOHA) 7th International Scientific Conference, “Anti-oxidation Capability and Environmental Factors for Noise Induced Permanent Hearing Loss”, Taipei, Taiwan, Feb., 2008.- 20.  Best Paper Award (Fifth Prize) in 2005 Occupational Health Conference, “Characteristics and Control of Free Silica Emissions from Maintenance Works in Construction Industry”, Tainan, Taiwan, April, 2005.- 21.  Best Paper Award (First Prize) in 2004 Occupational Health Conference, “Emissions of VOCs from Motor Vehicle Engines under Various Driving Conditions”, Kaohsiung, Taiwan, April, 2004.- 22.  Best Paper Award in 2004 Occupational Health Conference, “Characteristics of PAH Emissions from Aircraft Engines”, Kaohsiung, Taiwan, April, 2004.- 23.  Best Paper Award in 2004 Occupational Health Conference, “Characteristics of Free Silica Exposures to Workers in Casting Industries”, Kaohsiung, Taiwan, April, 2004.- 24.  Best Paper Award in 2004 Occupational Health Conference, “Exposure and Health Risk Assessment for PAH Exposures to Steel Industry Workers”, Kaohsiung, Taiwan, April, 2004.顯示更多 



